1. Establish daily goals for each team member
2. Break daily goals down to hourly sprints
3. At the start of each hour, have a 2 minute scrum for each person to say what they are working on for that hour
4. At the end of each hour, have a 5 minute scrum to identify: 
  A. what each person has accomplished, 
  B. Any conflicts in dependencies between different group members
  C. Any areas where effort levels need to be adjusted
  D. Any areas where we can help with debugging/learning
  
Daily Morning standup 30 minutes after hacking time begins
Daily evening standup following dinner
  
We will follow the CONTRIBUTING.md process strictly, except for updates to the docs. 
